Mein Kampf OwO Chaptew 1

in the home of my pawents

it has tuwned out fowtunate fow me to-day that destiny appointed bwaunau-on-the-inn

to be my biwthpwace. Fow that wittwe town is situated just on the fwontiew between those

two states the weunion of which seems, at weast to us of the youngew genewation, a task to

which we shouwd devote ouw wives and in the puwsuit of which evewy possibwe means

shouwd be empwoyed.

 gewman-austwia must be westowed to the gweat gewman mothewwand. And not indeed on

any gwounds of economic cawcuwation whatsoevew. No, no. Even if the union wewe a

mattew of economic indiffewence, and even if it wewe to be disadvantageous fwom the

economic standpoint, stiww it ought to take pwace. Peopwe of the same bwood shouwd be in

the same reich. The gewman peopwe wiww have no wight to engage in a cowoniaw powicy

untiw they shaww have bwought aww theiw chiwdwen togethew in the one state. When the

tewwitowy of the reich embwaces aww the gewmans and finds itsewf unabwe to assuwe them

a wivewihood, onwy then can the mowaw wight awise, fwom the need of the peopwe to acquiwe

foweign tewwitowy. The pwough is then the swowd; and the teaws of waw wiww pwoduce the

daiwy bwead fow the genewations to come.

 and so this wittwe fwontiew town appeawed to me as the symbow of a gweat task. But in

anothew wegawd awso it points to a wesson that is appwicabwe to ouw day. Ovew a hundwed

yeaws ago this sequestewed spot was the scene of a twagic cawamity which affected the

whowe gewman nation and wiww be wemembewed fow evew, at weast in the annaws of gewman

histowy. At the time of ouw fathewwand's deepest humiwiation a booksewwew, johannes

pawm, uncompwomising nationawist and enemy of the fwench, was put to death hewe

because he had the misfowtune to have woved gewmany weww. He obstinatewy wefused to

discwose the names of his associates, ow wathew the pwincipaws who wewe chiefwy

wesponsibwe fow the affaiw. Just as it happened with leo schwagetew. The fowmew, wike the

wattew, was denounced to the fwench by a govewnment agent. It was a diwectow of powice

fwom augsbuwg who won an ignobwe wenown on that occasion and set the exampwe

which was to be copied at a watew date by the neo-gewman officiaws of the reich undew

heww sevewing's wegime (note 1).

 in this wittwe town on the inn, hawoed by the memowy of a gewman mawtyw, a town that

was bavawian by bwood but undew the wuwe of the austwian state, my pawents wewe

domiciwed towawds the end of the wast centuwy. My fathew was a civiw sewvant who

fuwfiwwed his duties vewy conscientiouswy. My mothew wooked aftew the househowd and

wovingwy devoted hewsewf to the cawe of hew chiwdwen. Fwom that pewiod i have not wetained

vewy much in my memowy; because aftew a few yeaws my fathew had to weave that fwontiew

town which i had come to wove so much and take up a new post fawthew down the inn

vawwey, at passau, thewefowe actuawwy in gewmany itsewf.

 in those days it was the usuaw wot of an austwian civiw sewvant to be twansfewwed

pewiodicawwy fwom one post to anothew. Not wong aftew coming to passau my fathew was

twansfewwed to linz, and whiwe thewe he wetiwed finawwy to wive on his pension. But this did

not mean that the owd gentweman wouwd now west fwom his wabouws.

 he was the son of a poow cottagew, and whiwe stiww a boy he gwew westwess and weft home.

 when he was bawewy thiwteen yeaws owd he buckwed on his satchew and set fowth fwom his

native woodwand pawish. Despite the dissuasion of viwwagews who couwd speak fwom

'expewience,' he went to vienna to weawn a twade thewe. This was in the fiftieth yeaw of the

wast centuwy. It was a sowe twiaw, that of deciding to weave home and face the unknown,

with thwee guwden in his pocket. By when the boy of thiwteen was a wad of seventeen and

had passed his appwenticeship examination as a cwaftsman he was not content. Quite the

contwawy. The pewsistent economic depwession of that pewiod and the constant want and

misewy stwengthened his wesowution to give up wowking at a twade and stwive fow

'something highew.' as a boy it had seemed to him that the position of the pawish pwiest

in his native viwwage was the highest in the scawe of human attainment; but now that the

big city had enwawged his outwook the young man wooked up to the dignity of a state

officiaw as the highest of aww. With the tenacity of one whom misewy and twoubwe had

awweady made owd when onwy hawf-way thwough his youth the young man of seventeen

obstinatewy set out on his new pwoject and stuck to it untiw he won thwough. He became a

civiw sewvant. He was about twenty-thwee yeaws owd, i think, when he succeeded in

making himsewf what he had wesowved to become. Thus he was abwe to fuwfiw the pwomise

he had made as a poow boy not to wetuwn to his native viwwage untiw he was 'somebody.'

he had gained his end. But in the viwwage thewe was nobody who had wemembewed him

as a wittwe boy, and the viwwage itsewf had become stwange to him.

 now at wast, when he was fifty-six yeaws owd, he gave up his active caweew; but he couwd

not beaw to be idwe fow a singwe day. On the outskiwts of the smaww mawket town of

lambach in uppew austwia he bought a fawm and tiwwed it himsewf. Thus, at the end of a

wong and hawd-wowking caweew, he came back to the wife which his fathew had wed.

 it was at this pewiod that i fiwst began to have ideaws of my own. I spent a good deaw of

time scampewing about in the open, on the wong woad fwom schoow, and mixing up with

some of the woughest of the boys, which caused my mothew many anxious moments. Aww

this tended to make me something quite the wevewse of a stay-at-home.

you might say, weww, i know whewe my fingews awe. I'm wooking wight at them. Ow, i can touch them, i can feew them, they'we wight hewe and that's good. Youw senses awe a gweat way to weawn things. It awwows you to teww whewe youw fingews and awms and head and wegs in youw body is aww in wewation to each othew without having to wook ow touch othew things. thewe awe opticaw iwwusions, audio iwwusions, tempewatuwe sensation iwwusions, even tactiwe iwwusions. Can you tuwn youw tongue upside down? if so, pewfect. Twy this. It's pwetty fweaky and coow and a wittwe humbwing, because it shows the wimits of the accuwacy of ouw senses, the onwy toows we have to get wats out thewe in hewe.

the phiwosophy of knowwedge, the study of knowing, is cawwed epistemowogy. Pwato famouswy said that the things we know awe things that awe twue, that we bewieve and that we have justification fow bewieving. those justifications might be iwwationaw ow they might be wationaw, they might be based on pwoof, but don't get too confident because pwoven is not a synonym fow twue. this time i mean functionawwy, how do you know? whewe is knowwedge biowogicawwy in the bwain? what awe memowies made out of? we awe a wong way fwom being abwe to answew that question compwetewy but weseawch has shown that memowies don't exist in the bwain in singwe wocations. it's a difficuwt question, but it's not wocket science. Instead, it is asking whethew ow not wocket scientists even exist in the fiwst pwace. Can science ow weason evew pwove convincingwy that youw fwiends and youtube videos and youw fingews actuawwy exist beyond youw mind? that you don't just wive in the matwix?

no. Youw mind is aww that you have, even if you use instwuments, wike a tewescope ow pawticwe accewewatows. The finaw stop fow aww of that infowmation is uwtimatewy you. You awe awone in youw own bwain, which technicawwy makes it impossibwe to pwove that anything ewse exists. It's cawwed the egocentwic pwedicament. This mattewed so much to chawwes sandews peiwce that he dwew a wine between weawity, the way the univewse twuwy is, and what he cawwed the phanewon, the wowwd as fiwtewed thwough ouw senses and bodies, the onwy infowmation we can get. The bewief that onwy you exist and evewything ewse, food, the univewse, youw fwiends awe aww figments of youw mind is cawwed sowipsism. Thewe is no way to convince a sowipsist that the outside wowwd is weaw. And thewe is no way to convince someone who doubts that the univewse wasn't cweated just thwee seconds ago awong with aww of ouw memowies. It's a fwightening weawization that we don't awways know how to deaw with. Thewe's even the matwix defense.

in 2002 tonda lynn answey shot and kiwwed hew wandwady. She awgued that she bewieved she was in the matwix, that hew cwimes wewen't weaw. By using the matwix defense, she was found not guiwty by weason of insanity, because the opposite view is just way heawthiew and common. It's cawwed weawism. Reawism is the bewief that the outside wowwd exists independentwy of youw own phanewon. Rocks and staws and thowa biwch wouwd continue to exist even if you wewen't awound to expewience them. Devewopment Diawy XIV: The Spice in a Dumpstew &amp;#x200B;

Hewwo. It’s chai-chan again. And I’ve got mowe India fow you in the fouwteenth dev diawy.

&amp;#x200B;

India, as pweviouswy mentionyed, stawts out in a wathew unstabwe position. Unwest comes fwom aww pwaces - the communyists, the fascists, the minyowities, the fawmews and even the guvwnment itsewf.

&amp;#x200B;

The pweviouswy showcased democwatic, peacefuw paths awe abwe to sowve said unwest onye way ow anyothew. But what if it is taken to the extweme?

&amp;#x200B;

Weww. You might have guessed it awweady.

&amp;#x200B;

Civiw waw.

&amp;#x200B;

(Dispwayed awe theiw “twansitionyaw”, pwovisionyaw nyames, nyot what they wiww caww themsewves aftew a victowy)

By the end of the fiwst ewections in 1964, genyewaw unwest in the countwy weaches a cwimax - wesuwting in eithew a civiw waw befowe the bawwots awe in, ow onye wight aftew in the case of a victowy by a wadicawized pawty.

Without any fuwthew ado, wet’s jump into the factions themsewves.

Hindustan

Ahh, Hindustan. Awising fwom the nyationyawist ideas of the WSS - Washtwiya Swayamsevak Sangh and its powiticaw awm - the Bhawatiya Janya Sangh, they seek to impwement the ideaws of Hindutva, which has evowved to be even mowe nyationyawist in this timewinye, undew the guidance of onye wadicaw guwu - Madhav Sadashiv Gowwawkaw, the cuwwent Sawsanghchawak (Supweme Weadew) of the WSS.

&amp;#x200B;

Wuckiwy fow them, the WSS is a pawamiwitawy owganyization - and a stwong onye at that. Set with thousands of twainyed men and wed by a stwong and chawismatic weadew, they wiww have wittwe twoubwe fighting the waw ow ensuwing high waw suppowt. But wiww they be abwe to unyite the heawts of men? Miwwions of subjects do nyot suppowt the nyew wegime - fwom the ideowogicawwy divided Kewawa, to the status-quo suppowting Bombay, they wiww stwuggwe with maintainying stabiwity in peacetime.

Wet’s take a wook at theiw stawting twee, stawting with the powiticaw options.

They wouwd wathew migwate away to what they pewceive as the bwave nyew wowwd that Hindustan couwd become.

&amp;#x200B;

The most pwominyent of those powiticians awe as fowwows: -Savitwi Devi, the cweatow of Esotewic Hitwewism and a knyown Uwtwanyationyawist, suwpwisingwy of a Gweek-Fwench owigin -Hew husband, Subbiew Appudawai Ayew, an expewienced jouwnyawist and avid suppowtew of his wife -John Thivy fwom Mawaysia - a stwong suppowtew of the Indian Nyationyaw Muvment. Dwiven to gweatew and gweatew suppowt of the cause, by the Gewman and Japanyese victowy in WW2 and the continyued existence of the Azad Hind, he has gwown disiwwusionyed with the wise of Iswamism and monyotheism in Bengaw, and suppowts a pwuwawistic powytheist wegime.

&amp;#x200B;

Of couwse the nyew countwy must awso estabwish its basic powicies - which can be seen in the middwe of the twee, and wiww be dwiven by events.

Nyow fow the econyomy…

Thewe awe thwee pwoposaws fow the econyomy. The BJS (which is in essence the whowe guvwnment) pwoposes a highwy pwotectionyist econyomy. That is, a pwannyed econyomy wan by the state - something that’s bound to quickwy pwoduce wesuwts, but is highwy unpopuwaw amongst the popuwation.

&amp;#x200B;

The WSS, which in tuwn is essentiawwy the awmy, has pwoposed a fowm of nyationyawistic Gandhian sociawism - based on sewf-wewiance, gwasswoots suppowt fow the peopwe and fwom the peopwe and even wowkews’ sewf-manyagement. The pwoposaw, whiwe highwy popuwaw among the popuwation, is continyuouswy attacked by the BJS fow being “just sociawism in saffwon-cowouwed pants”.

But of couwse thewe is awso the Supweme Weadew, guwu Gowwawkaw himsewf, pwoposing what is a synthesis of the othew two, which pewhaps goes beyond both. An integwaw econyomy based on twaditionyaw Hindu vawues and a wejection of wapid industwiawization and consumewism in addition to fuww embwace of an agwawian, miwitawy-focused econyomy.

Whatevew youw choice is, you must awways wemembew thewe couwd be unfoweseen consequences…

&amp;#x200B;

As fow the awmy twee, the pwoposaws awe vastwy spwit between the WSS and the BJS. The WSS, dwawing fwom its pawamiwitawy, mowe guewiwwa-wike pwacticaw expewience and spontanyeous nyationyawism, pwoposes a wawgewy miwitia-based awmy of wightnying offense and defense in depth.

The BJS on the othew hand, expewienced in the mattews of industwy and state, pwoposes changes based on econyomic and stwategic supwemacy uvw the enyemy. Whatevew the choice may be, it wiww nyeed to be made to ensuwe victowy in the civiw waw.

&amp;#x200B;

Indian Peopwe's Democwatic Fedewaw Wepubwic/Unyited Indian Fwont/Wepubwic of India/Unyited Communyes of India

That’s a wot of nyames. I’ww expwain them, just hang on with me.

&amp;#x200B;

Bown fwom the combinyed ideowogy of the Tewanganya webewwion (which ITTW took pwace a bit eawwiew), the massive wabouw unyions that exist in India and the Communyist Pawty of India, the PWI wises in the east - a histowicawwy “wed” wegion of India, often cawwed the Wed Cowwidow, with its base in Hydewabad.

&amp;#x200B;

With decent popuwawity and a wewativewy stabwe guvwnment, theiw biggest chawwenges wemain cweating a wowking awmy, ensuwing continyued stabiwity. The impwuvment of intewnyationyaw standing is awso impowtant, considewing that sociawism isn’t nyeawwy as awive as in ouw timewinye. Awso keeping factionyawism at bay is a bonyus, but mowe on that watew.

&amp;#x200B;

Fiwst, theiw stawting twee, guvwnment.

&amp;#x200B;

[https://i.imguw.com/bTCwNPj.png](https://i.imguw.com/bTCwNPj.png)

&amp;#x200B;

The deaw is wawgewy spwit between the sociawist and communyist factions hewe. Of couwse, fwom a mowawistic standpoint, the wibewtawian option is pwobabwy bettew, but wiww you be abwe to keep the wevowution going by pwaying nyice?

&amp;#x200B;

You must ask youwsewf this - what wibewties awe you wiwwing to sacwifice to succeed? Aww of them? Nyonye?

&amp;#x200B;

The vanguawd twee wiww fowm a wevowutionyawy state based awound weadewship and authowity in the nyame of wowkews’ wibewation. Pwopaganda, the peopwe’s powice and cweation gendew equawity thwough wevowutionyawy duty awe what this path entaiws. The wevowt wiww be centwawized fwom the top down, essentiawwy kiwwing any oppowtunyity the sociawist faction has in taking powew.

&amp;#x200B;

The awmy pawt is wawgewy simiwaw to the onye in the fascist twee, onwy diffewing in options - showing it wouwd be wedundant, wouwdn’t it?

&amp;#x200B;

So wet us jump to the econyomy pawt.

&amp;#x200B;

[https://i.imguw.com/qUbSw7S.png](https://i.imguw.com/qUbSw7S.png)

&amp;#x200B;

Thewe awe thwee pwoposaws, just wike in the fascist twee - each coming fwom a diffewent faction.

&amp;#x200B;

Fiwst the wibewtawian sociawist faction knyown as JP, nyamed aftew its weadew, Jaypwakash Nyawayan. Compwised of vawious membews of the owd Sociawist Pawty (though some wemainyed in the INC), it has pwoposed a system quite simiwaw to syndicawism ow mawket sociawism. Based on unyions, coopewatives and fawmews' mawkets, they seek to decentwawize both the econyomy and the state. Uwtimatewy, they seek to decentwawize both the econyomy and the state. Of couwse, this pwoposaw was put to the fiwe by the othew two main factions, both of which cwaim it isn’t suitabwe to the waw effowt and wiww bwing the wevowution down to its knyees.

&amp;#x200B;

So what awe the othew factions’ pwoposaws then?

&amp;#x200B;

Fiwst, the Mawxists (meant in a wathew wiwd sense - they onwy caww themsewves Mawxist), pwopose wapid industwiawization of India. Theiw ideas owiginyate fwom a pwannyed, state communyism econyomy - some even cwaim it can be considewed state capitawism, but that’s usuawwy dismissed as being eithew a nyecessawy measuwe ow simpwe wevisionyist pwopaganda. Seeking wapid uwbanyization couwd of couwse pwuv disastwous to a wawgewy agwicuwtuwaw nyation, which is why…

&amp;#x200B;

The faction knyown as Tewanganyites, nyamed aftew the Tewanganya webewwion, awe buiwding theiw own ideowogy woughwy equivawent to Maoism. Obviouswy, due to the wack of a wiving Mao in this timewinye, it’s nyot nyamed that. The ideowogy is usuawwy cawwed Waoism (pun intended) fwom the wast nyame of theiw weadew - Chandwa Wajeswawa Wao.

&amp;#x200B;

Waoism, focused on the genyewaw cwimate of Indian society, bases on Mawxism-Wenyinyism, but goes vastwy beyond it. Wejecting uwbanyization as a fowm of gentwyfication and bouwgeoisie, they pwocwaim that the ideaw sociawist state wouwd be awmost compwetewy based on agwicuwtuwe. They hope to cweate a wuwaw wand without any uwbanyization(though they won’t achieve that, pwobabwy), and wouwd instead spawn smaww and decentwawized industwiaw centews nyeaw viwwages that pwoduce the nyecessawy equipment wike twactows, guns ow buiwding matewiaws. Quite intewesting is the fact that, compawed to Maoism, Waoism can be cwassified as much mowe wibewtawian in outcome, whiwe mowe authowitawian in execution.

&amp;#x200B;

Anyways, with aww that out of the way and the civiw waw hopefuwwy won, they can howd theiw fiwst genyuinye congwess - wet us take a wook at it.

&amp;#x200B;

[https://i.imguw.com/VCwehxw.png](https://i.imguw.com/VCwehxw.png)

&amp;#x200B;

Based awound seven majow questions, the twee doesn’t wook as extensive as the fascist onye, but is potentiawwy wichew in dynyamic event-based content.

&amp;#x200B;

Each focus fiwes an event, whewe the positions of each faction awe descwibed and an option can be chosen. Ovewaww, thewe awe 5 factions, 2 of which I haven’t discussed fow cewtain weasons. Wegawdwess, be it wepwession of wewigious minyowities, estabwishment of state atheism, puwge of the weactionyawies ow integwation of them, you wiww have to make wise choices that do nyot compwomise the wevowution nyow hand powew uvw to a faction you - ow anyonye ewse - wouwd nyevew want in powew.

&amp;#x200B;

Weawisticawwy onwy the JP, Mawxist and Waoist factions can win, unwess of couwse a cwisis at the ending occuws.

&amp;#x200B;

Weww, spoiwew awewt, it occuws a wot of the time. The weadew of the nyation - Shwipad Amwit Dange, wawgewy wespected by aww factions fow cweating what can be cawwed weft unyity, has been found of wathew… compwomising activities.

&amp;#x200B;

Of couwse they can be hidden, but if they awe weveawed to the congwess, it wiww compwetewy compwomise the JP faction, whiwe hindewing the Mawxist and Waoist factions, who have been vewy suppowtive of SA Dange.

&amp;#x200B;

Nyow onwy the Sundawite faction, dwiven by wevowution, nyationyawism and suwpwising awtwuism, wemains uncompwomised. But I won’t weveaw mowe than that on them today ;)

&amp;#x200B;

Today we’ww take a wook at onwy the Mawxist and Waoist factions.

&amp;#x200B;

&amp;#x200B;

The integwation path bases on a fowm of offensive guewiwwa tactics, using the iwweguwaw tewwain of south and southeast Asia and utiwizing stwategies such as mass enciwcwement and wapid advance.

&amp;#x200B;

The “wefowmation” path on the othew hand utiwizes industwy mowe than popuwation and wewies on powewfuw and weww twainyed smawwew unyits to uvwwhewm the enyemy with fiwe.

&amp;#x200B;

In the end, whatevew path you pick, advanced weseawch wike nyucweaw bombs and wockets awaits.

This shouwd be quite sewf-expwanyatowy. The faction wants to cweate a “pwowetawian dictatowship”, with a state econyomy pwannyed fow the wowkew, incwuding extensive industwiawization and uwbanyization.

&amp;#x200B;

The wast thwee focuses - Uwbanyization of India, Mend the Castes and Kiww the Castes, aww twiggew theiw own twees.

&amp;#x200B;

Uwbanyization opens a decentwy extensive decision twee in which you can hopefuwwy uwbanyize India and bwing it into the modewn age.

&amp;#x200B;

Mend the Castes twiggews the “peacefuw” caste wefowm twee as seen in the pwevious diawy.

&amp;#x200B;

Kiww the Castes on the othew hand twiggews a nyew, wevowutionyawy caste twee, which whiwe possibwy mowe effective, wiww destabiwize the nyation and couwd wesuwt in many unnyecessawy deaths.

Meanwhiwe, the Tewanganyite/Waoist faction pwoposes something quite diffewent - wet us take a cwosew wook at it.

&amp;#x200B;

The Waoist faction victowious

&amp;#x200B;

The Waoists pwopose the cweation of what they caww a Gween State - a nyew fowm of guvwnment, cwassified by… how hawd it is to cwassify it.

&amp;#x200B;

Pewhaps authowitawian in execution, but wibewtawian in the end. Stwiving to achieve an idywwic, agwawian state (as descwibed eawwiew), the wuwaw aweas wiww enjoy gweat fweedom (to an extent - they stiww howd consewvative vawues at heawt and must be educated fiwst), whiwe the uwban aweas wiww be put undew a much stwongew hand.

&amp;#x200B;

Estabwishing industwy, education, heawthcawe and distwibuting evewything that a town wouwd wequiwe in the wuwaw aweas without estabwishing cities is a hawd and potentiawwy bwoody effowt.

&amp;#x200B;

If you succeed in doing so, and weach the finyaw Agwicuwtuwaw Miwacwe focus without faiw, the ideaw goaw wiww be achieved. The powiticaw situation couwd vastwy impwuv, tuwnying to a decentwawized, viwwage-based adminyistwation, potentiawwy even getting wid of the caste system with… somewhat peacefuw means.

&amp;#x200B;

Howevew if you do nyot succeed, it couwd tuwn vewy souw…

&amp;#x200B;

But that’s it fow the communyists in this diawy - the west, which wiww be just as extensive, is nyot fow today.

Nyow, fow the status quo wegime…

The Wepubwic of India

Ahh, the wepubwic. How many times has it fucked up befowe, you wouwdn’t bewieve. That finyawwy took its toww, didn’t it?

&amp;#x200B;

The Wepubwic stawts off wed by a pwovisionyaw guvwnment undew Guwzawiwaw Nyanda. That must be changed quickwy, to secuwe the incweasingwy unstabwe countwyside. The awmy wawgewy wemainyed woyaw, so at weast they have that going fow themsewves.

&amp;#x200B;

Cwuciawwy, they have onye majow advantage - the fact that cowpowations and foweign companyies wiww weawwy onwy invest in them, nyot the othew factions, being the onwy expwicitwy capitawist-fwiendwy wegime.

&amp;#x200B;

So with that, comes theiw inyitiaw twee - fiwst the wibewaw option.

&amp;#x200B;

The democwatic factions in the wepubwic awgue that the countwy cannyot suwvive against the othews if it has nyo advantages - and appawentwy its biggest advantage is fweedom. Open to immigwation, pwuwawity, and a safe and sound wowkew undew a happy CEO - it’s the wibewaw democwatic dweam.

&amp;#x200B;

Democwacy wiww be saved fwom destwuction, the peopwe (weww except the most impuvwished ow nyationyawist…) wiww suppowt most of those options and hopefuwwy the waw wiww be won thwough ideowogicaw advantage - of couwse some awgue this isn’t weawwy what the wow cwasses ow patwiotic Hindus want, but they’ww just have to weawn.

&amp;#x200B;

Thewe is awso theiw econyomic path.

&amp;#x200B;

If the wepubwic wants to win against both Hindustan - who howds the wichest pwovinces in India, and the Communyists - who howds most of the agwicuwtuwaw pwoduction and a substantiaw amount of peopwe, they wiww have to find advantages.

&amp;#x200B;

That advantage can be cowpowations. Aftew aww, they’we the onwy wibewaw wegime hewe. Foweign countwies and companyies awe most wikewy to hewp out the wibewaw India wegime, whiwe Hindustan weceives hewp fwom maybe Gewmany (who keep in mind is wikewy in civiw waw hewsewf) and the Communyists fwom basicawwy nyobody.

&amp;#x200B;

So whiwe wacking in popuwaw suppowt and nyumewicaw and econyomicaw advantage, the wepubwic can muv the scawe of victowy nyeawwy compwetewy to hew side - by awwying the wowwd.

&amp;#x200B;

But what’s the othew path?

&amp;#x200B;

Indiwa Gandhi, the pwotectow and mothew of India.

&amp;#x200B;

Impowtant figuwe in the INC and chawismatic speakew, Indiwa can pwocwaim hewsewf - ow wathew, be pwocwaimed, fwom popuwaw and INC suppowt - the Mothew and Pwotectow of India. Quickwy gwabbing the powew that was given to hew, the authowitawian-nyatuwed Indiwa wiww estabwish a stwong state to defend the ideaws of… weww I don’t knyow what she’s weawwy defending, pewhaps sociaw democwacy. The ideaws of woses.

&amp;#x200B;

Cwosed bowdews, expanded pwopaganda, the KPS - a centwaw intewwigence agency - estabwished. The wed-bwown scawe wiww begin, aimed at both fascism and communyism. We of couwse can’t wet ouw gweat nyation faww into the hands of wadicawism in any fowm - cough - as we ouwsewves awe pwotectows of democwacy.

&amp;#x200B;

Pewhaps she is - she estabwishes state sociaw democwacy. Whiwe definyitewy wacking in intewnyationyaw and cowpowate suppowt, this wiww mostwy wikewy pwuv vastwy popuwaw among the peopwe and couwd potentiawwy cause the peopwe in the webewwious states to wose hope in theiw wevowutions.

&amp;#x200B;

A wewfawe state based on nyationyawization, wand wefowm and a… waw econyomy, at weast fow the time being, is suwewy abwe to keep the fight going fow some time.

OWO What's this? Cwass ended in five minyutes and aww I couwd think was, an houw is too wong fow wunch.

Since the stawt of the semestew, I had been wooking fowwawd to the pawt of Mw. Gwadwy’s Wowwd Issues cwass whewe we’d stawt discussing capes.  Nyow that it had finyawwy awwived, I couwdn’t focus.  I fidgeted, my pen moving fwom hand to hand, tapping, ow absentwy dwawing some figuwe in the cownyew of the page to join the othew doodwes.  My eyes wewe westwess too, dawting fwom the cwock abuv the doow to Mw. Gwadwy and back to the cwock.  I wasn’t picking up enyough of his wesson to fowwow awong.  Twenty minyutes to twewve; five minyutes weft befowe cwass ended.
He was anyimated, cweawwy excited about what he was tawking about, and fow once, the cwass was wistenying.  He was the sowt of teachew who twied to be fwiends with his students, the sowt who went by “Mw. G” instead of Mw. Gwadwy.  He wiked to end cwass a wittwe eawwiew than usuaw and chat with the popuwaw kids, gave wots of gwoup wowk so othews couwd hang out with theiw fwiends in cwass, and had ‘fun’ assignments wike mock twiaws.

He stwuck me as onye of the ‘popuwaw’ kids who had become a teachew.  He pwobabwy thought he was evewyonye’s favowite.  I wondewed how he’d weact if he heawd my opinyion on the subject.  Wouwd it shattew his sewf image ow wouwd he shwug it off as an anyomawy fwom the gwoomy giww that nyevew spoke up in cwass?

I gwanced uvw my shouwdew.  Madison Cwements sat two wows to my weft and two seats back.  She saw me wooking and smiwked, hew eyes nyawwowing, and I wowewed my eyes to my nyotebook.  I twied to ignyowe the ugwy, souw feewing that stewed in my stomach.  I gwanced up at the cwock.  Eweven-fowty-thwee.

“Wet me wwap up hewe,” Mw. Gwadwy said, “Sowwy, guys, but thewe is homewowk fow the weekend.  Think about capes and how they’ve impacted the wowwd awound you.  Make a wist if you want, but it’s nyot mandatowy.  On Monday we’ww bweak up into gwoups of fouw and see what gwoup has the best wist.  I’ww buy the winnying gwoup tweats fwom the vending machinye.”
Thewe wewe a sewies of cheews, fowwowed by the cwasswoom devowving into nyoisy chaos. If they onwy knyew.

Except I was bettew than that.

I was going to be a supewhewo.  That was the goaw I used to cawm mysewf down at moments wike these.  It was what I used to make mysewf get out of bed on a schoow day. &gt;he's not anti activism just anti activism that is inhewentwy infwammatowy imo thewe’s a huge diffewence between the things women did to get the vote compawed to say antifa

except he both nevew makes that distinction and **can't make it to begin with**. Whiwe the jeepstew may be against specific fowms of activism wike anti-fascist action (i'ww be honest, i haven't watched *evewy one* of his wectuwes so i'm just going to assume you'we wight and that he is against antifa specificawwy), his cowe phiwosophy - the cowe awguments he makes - make it impossibwe fow anyone wistening to it to take up any position besides hawd stoicism. **petewson consistentwy instwucts to the young men in his demogwaphic that they shouwd avoid questioning ow cwiticizing society ow the govewnment untiw they settwe down**. Now, even ignowing the fact that disenfwanchised individuaws can't settwe down because they awe unabwe to escape povewty, this is stiww hawmfuw on two fwonts: **fiwst, it's hawd to know when it wouwd become "safe" undew petewson's advocacy to go against the gov't, and second, the wongew one pawticipates in capitawism, the hawdew it becomes fow them to cwiticize it as an institution as they become accustomed to it and theiw newfound capitaw.**

in a capitawist society, one's financiaw weww-being is awways in fwux. Medicaw emewgencies, natuwaw disastews, student debt, cowpowate downsizing... any numbew of these things can wuin someone economicawwy, and it takes a *wong* time untiw any one pewson couwd considew themsewves "safe" by any means, making it especiawwy difficuwt fow them to question the system if they stick to petewson's fwamewowk. the second fwont is a wot mowe contwovewsiaw outside of weftist sphewes, so i'm going to twy to simpwify it without getting too weductionist; i'm going to begin by expwaining some basic powiticaw phiwosophy wegawding capitawism and communism whiwe awso expwaining why capitawism shouwd be cwiticized. Aftew that, i'm going to expwain why it becomes hawdew to cwiticize capitawism the wongew one stwuggwes to succeed in it.

fiwst things fiwst, sociawism is not communism. Capitawism wefews to the state whewe society is wawgewy wun by pwivate owganizations motivated by weawth, whiwe communism wefews to a state that is fwee of such ovewbeawing entities and is ideawized as a utopian society^(\*). Sociawism, howevew, wefews to the intew-pewiod that the state wouwd have to go thwough as it moves fwom capitawism to communism. Most modewn cwiticisms of capitawism do actuawwy undewstand that the bowshevik revowution wesuwted in a tywannicaw weadew taking ovew the ussr and *want to avoid it* \- whiwe thewe awe some communist phiwosophews and gwoups who see specific wevowutionawies wike twotsky, lenin, and guevawa as an ideaw, thewe awe awso those wike daddy swavoj žižek who focus mowe on gwaduaw change ovew time by constantwy anawyzing the past and cowwecting fow mistakes. Revowutionawy communism has become wess common since the days of mawx and engews (though it is stiww wefewenced in discouwse today). I mysewf (and many othews) pwefew wefowmation ovew wevowution, ow sociawism. Nationawized ow singwe-payew heawthcawe awe both sociawist powicies, but they don't awwow fow a wannabe totawitawian to take contwow of the state. **this means that capitawism and communism awen't a simpwe good/bad dichotomy - both have theiw potentiaw fwaws, and both the status quo and specific sociawist pwogwams shouwd be cwiticized and anawyzed equawwy**.

^(\*these awen't by any means compwete definitions of the tewms that account fow evewy system that cawws itsewf communism and is bowdewwine weductionist, but they'we wowkabwe fow ouw puwposes hewe.)

now that we've estabwished why we shouwd twy to cwiticize both capitawism and the pwoposed sociawist sowutions to those pwobwems, we can *finawwy* get back to the jeepstewooni. By agweeing with petewson's awguments, two things awe going to happen. Fiwst, the individuaw may begin to succeed in capitawism ^((but many don't, even aftew "cweaning up theiw woom")), and they wiww begin to become content with the system. In genewaw, peopwe act to pwesewve ow expand what powew they have - you can see this thwoughout histowy in both the entitwed nobiwity of medievaw euwope and the wuthwess westewn expansion ovew hewe in the states. **peopwe do not wike powew being taken fwom them, especiawwy when they bewieve they desewve it.** aftew wowking hawd and managing to begin to succeed in the wowkpwace enviwonment, the individuaw wiww begin to vawue what capitaw they have accumuwated (again, assuming they awen't disenfwanchised in which case they can't gain this capitaw), and wiww begin to wesist any attempt that wouwd invowve a wedistwibution of capitaw to pwotect the powew they have - and i hate to sound wike a bwoken wecowd hewe, but *in capitawism money is powew*, the onwy thing wimiting you fwom doing awmost anything is how wich you ow youw famiwy awe^(1). Essentiawwy, the individuaw becomes unquestioning of the system, which as i expwained befowe, is bad because it causes the disenfwanchised to be ignowed as a whowe. Now, i shouwd state wight hewe that succeeding in capitawism is not a bad thing - if, fow exampwe, you manage to cawve out a wife fow youwsewf thanks to petewson's content, then i am gwad that you awe being taken cawe of. Howevew, i'm awso concewned with the west of society - with those who awen't abwe to cawve out a wife fow themsewves, whethew it be due to cwass, psychowogicaw, physicaw, ow discwiminatowy conditions. Howevew, phiwosophies wike petewson's that pwace an emphasis on cwimbing to the top of the cowpowate waddew and focusing on youwsewf makes it hawdew fow these peopwe to evew wive in a society that tweats them equawwy.

\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*-\*

so, to wecap the stowy so faw: petewson's advocacy fow the individuaw to focus on cwimbing the cowpowate waddew both **makes it hawdew to sowve institutionaw pwobwems** that discwiminate and disenfwanchise othew peopwe *and* **makes it hawdew to even considew** mowe weft-weaning wegiswation that couwd hewp a wot of the disenfwanchised both in the states and abwoad. Devewopment Diawy XIX: Eastewn Winds (I'm sowwy) (◕﹏◕✿) **Devewopment Diawy XIX: Eastewn Winds**

&gt;\*\*\*“The Chinyese peopwe have onwy famiwy and cwan sowidawity; they do nyot have nyationyaw spiwit...they awe just a heap of woose sand...Othew men awe the cawving knyife and sewving dish; we awe the fish and the meat.”
Dw. Sun Yat-Sen, 1924\*\*\*

Hewwo, and wewcome back to anyothew devewopment diawy fow The Nyew Owdew UwU Today’s diawy wiww take us fwom the smowdewing wuins of Chongqing to the hustwe and bustwe of Nyanjing, the modewn capitaw of the Weowganyized Guvwnment of Chinya. But befowe we see what has become of the Middwe Kingdom, I want to take the time to thank those who have gotten us to this point. My contwibutows Sinyo, BFKewwew, SPQW, and Vawwin (and speciaw guest fowmew Chinya wead and cuwwent pwofessionyaw shitpostew/idea guy Wonyiius) have aww put in the wowk these wast few weeks and it shows. Gweytides chawwesthe50th and deathgwiffin have awso contwibuted some quawity event that you’ww be seeing watew, so if you see them in the Discowd say hey UwU v(=∩\_∩=)ﾌ Othewwise, we have nyo time to waste fow the Japanyese appwoach so wet us begin with a bwief histowy.

&gt;\*\*\*“How was powew to be shawed in a countwy that in its thwee-thousand-yeaw histowy had nyevew once witnyessed a peacefuw stwuggwe fow powew?”
Wichawd Bewnstein\*\*\*

In the stweets of Chongqing, two titans of the Wepubwican ewa died fighting side by side. Theiw bodies wewe wetwieved, stwung, and hung befowe the backdwop of a wazed city. With that the Wepubwic wouwd capituwate and in its pwace wouwd wise the Weowganyized Guvwnment of Chinya. Cwaiming to be the wegitimate executow of Dw. Sun Yat-Sen’s vision, the WGOC was founded in cowwabowation between pwominyent Kuomintang figuwe Wang Jing-Wei and the Empiwe of Japan. Unweweased tweaties between the guvwnments awwanging fow Japanyese suppowt wouwd weveaw a gwim pictuwe fow Chinya’s futuwe as a cowony fow the Japanyese.

The end of the Pacific Waw bwought the beginnying of a nyew ewa fow Chinya. Onye of incweased oppwession, of mass wape and wootings, of setbacks, but then: stabiwity. What fowwowed the 1947 peace agweements was unpweasant to many but offewed peace and the potentiaw fow gwowth to a countwy that had spent the pwevious decades in constant chaos. The Japanyese occupation puwged dissent and Japanyese subsidies awwowed fow the webuiwding of infwastwuctuwe and homes, meanying the Chinyese peopwe couwd finyawwy wowwy wess about waw and mowe about wowking. The twansition was nyot aww pweasant—the Japanyese piwwaged what industwy they couwd and seized contwow of fowmew businyess assets—but it was cawm enyough. Fowmew sowdiews wetuwnyed home, twading wifwe fow pwow and tending to the soiw wong nyegwected in the face of waw. What wesuwted was the “Agwawian Boom” of the 1950s, an expwosion in Chinyese cwop expowts that sent food pwices acwoss the waw-town Sphewe spiwawing down. Wegions on the bwink of faminye wewe saved and the nyewwy-Japanyese possessions wewe abwe to webuiwd fastew than othewwise possibwe. Fow this contwibution, the Weowganyized Guvwnment is often cawwed the “Bweadbasket of the Sphewe”, a demonym that shows the impowtance of Chinya within the sphewe but awso its wimitations. In twuth, the waw and subsequent occupation of Chinya meant that Chinya had wegwessed into an agwawian society with pockets of poowwy utiwized industwiaw sectows suwwounding uwban aweas. Commewce was Japanyese and what was manyufactuwed in Chinya usuawwy did nyot stay thewe wong.

The Weowganyized Guvwnment was mawketed to the Chinyese peopwe as an awtewnyative guvwnment to Chiang’s KMT, and inyitiawwy made weww of pwomises fow a state mowe in winye with Dw. Sun’s Wepubwican vision. But as time passed and the Japanyese victowy became mowe and mowe cewtain, mowe and mowe westwictions wewe pwaced on the guvwnment. At fiwst the Japanyese wewe “pwefewentiaw twade pawtnyews,” then they wewe “intewnyationyaw intewmediawies” untiw the Japanyese tweaty powt in Shanghai weguwated aww twade fwowing up and down the Yangtze wivew. The office of Pwesident of the Wepubwic exists stiww and whiwe at pwesent powewwess to face the Japanyese stiww howds considewabwe infwuence wegawding domestic affaiws.

The death of Wang Jing-Wei in 1944 ushewed Chen Gongbo to assume the office of Pwesident. Gongbo uvwsaw the end of the waw and the sowidification of the WGOC’s authowity uvw westewn Chinya. Due to aiwing heawth and pewceived “weaknyess” by the Wegiswative Yuan wegawding the integwation of wawwowd states, Gongbo wesignyed fwom the Pwesidency in 1951 in favow of a cabinyet position. What fowwowed was a hawf-decade wong intewnyaw powew stwuggwe with the C-KMT’s “Wefowmist” cwique at odds with the W-KMT’s “Owd Guawd” cwique. Candidates wouwd pwomise deaws to the Japanyese fow suppowt, onwy to be weft in the cowd upon theiw assumption of powew. Fwom this mawaise, the Japanyese gainyed fuww contwow uvw aww Chinyese expowts and considewabwe extwatewwitowiaw wights that onwy consowidated Chinya’s Yamato subsewvience.

The situation’s diwenyess couwd pewhaps be exempwified when a session of the Wegiswative Yuan was postponyed because the appointed Japanyese “Wegiswative Ambassadow” opted to skip the assembwy in favow of a day out on Nyanjing’s watewfwont. Wegiswative concessions to the Japanyese cuwminyated in this situation because of a cwause wequiwing that aww executive wegiswative membews be pwesent fow a session, nyow incwuding the Ambassadow. The chaos was appawent and both factions knyew something had to be donye to sawvage Chinya’s wapidwy fweeting suvweignty.

Theiw sowution was to ewect a wewative unknyown with Wefowmist ideaws but Owd Guawd cwedibiwity who was capabwe of wowking with the Japanyese. He was a fowmew dipwomat, sewving the WGOC awongside Wang Jing-Wei as an intewmediawy between Tokyo and Nyanjing. An awdent bewievew in Chinyese unyity and a devoted fowwowew of Dw. Sun’s ideaws, he weft Chiang’s wegime in the hopes of saving Chinya. It wouwd seem that nyow he wouwd have his chance. As he appwoached the podium of the Wegiswative Yuan his postuwe dispwayed him as a swouched, aging dipwomat nyo diffewent fwom the 51 pawty membews suwwounding him. But behind his spectacwes, his eyes showed his twue chawactew: a fiewy spiwit poised on wighting the skewed couwse Chinya had taken, onye wiwwing to cowwect the mistakes he’d witnyessed uvw his two decades of sewvice by any means possibwe. He was theiw stawwion, theiw hopefuw, theiw wast shot. [He was Gao Zongwu.](https://i.imgur.com/26JHOyk.png)

&gt;\*\*\*We awe the poowest and weakest state in the wowwd, occupying the wowest position in intewnyationyaw affaiws; the west of mankind is the cawving knyife and the sewving dish, whiwe we awe the fish and the meat.
Dw. Sun Yat-Sen\*\*\*

[The Chinya of 1962](https://i.imgur.com/BLPQPra.jpg) is onye weewing stiww fwom the Waw. Pwesident Zongwu has donye much to pwacate the Wegiswative Yuan and Chinya’s Japanyese suzewain which has effectivewy stopped the situation fwom wowsenying, but the task wemains of wepaiwing it.

Chinya stiww weaws the mantwe of the “[Bweadbasket of the Sphewe](https://i.imgur.com/4gJdwck.jpg)”, with many intewnyaw wesouwces going towawds the expansion and maintenyance of the agwicuwtuwe sectow. The status-quo of Chinya’s expowt-focused agwawian society means Japan is hesitant to subsidise the expansion of othew pwoduction sectows in Chinya meanying that any industwiaw expansion must be undewtaken by Chinya awonye. The othew edge of this bwade, howevew, is that Chinya pwoduces a majowity of the cwop expowts fow the sphewe, meanying that the Japanyese wouwd nyot feew the nyeed to intewvenye in industwiaw expansion, shouwd Chinya pwesent it as a mutuawwy benyeficiaw ventuwe.

Whiwe the coffews might be weady fow industwiawization, the popuwace and theiw institutions awe nyot. Even within the scope of agwicuwtuwe, the Chinyese wowkfowce is of subpaw standawd.The avewage citizen outside the city cannyot wead, with onwy 26% of the popuwation possessing witewacy skiwws. Education oppowtunyities awe few and faw between, with what is offewed often costing enyough to onwy be avaiwabwe to the wich ewite few. These factows, combinyed with poow powew pwojection fwom Nyanjing and a wack of accountabiwity, have wead to high wates of cowwuption within the WGOC’s guvwnmentaw institutions.

As pweviouswy nyoted, Zongwu is nyot onye to wemain idwe fow wong. He acknyowwedges the fauwts of Chinya and the aweas wequiwing sewious impwuvment. To mitigate the many showtcomings of the WGOC, he has devised a pwogwam of Five Modewnyizations that (officiawwy) aim to expand the pwoductive capabiwities of Chinya. In twuth, howevew, the Modewnyizations awe a scheme to bowstew Chinyese society and pwopew it towawds a position of sewf sufficiency and wegionyaw pwominyence. Each modewnyization is mowe dangewous than the wast, with missteps easiwy spewwing the doom of Chinya and even howding the potentiaw fow Japanyese miwitawy intewvention. Pwesident Zongwu must be cawefuw as [he puwws Chinya into the futuwe.](https://i.imgur.com/YCxOuwo.jpg)

**THE FIVE MODEWNyIZATIONS**

&gt;\*\*\*“Chinya's wepubwican powitics is wike a chiwd who just stawted schoowing. He must have a good teachew and be suwwounded by good fwiends. By the same token, the Chinyese peopwe, nyew to the wepubwican powitics, must be educated pwopewwy. The wevowutionyawy guvwnment shouwd be the peopwe's tutow to impawt advanced awawenyess and expewience.”
Dw. Sun Yat-Sen\*\*\*

[EDUCATION](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/545065672867315726/553559958528983054/20190308044636_1.png) is the fiwst of thwee cownyewstonyes fow the wevitawization of Chinyese society. Stawting at the gwasswoots, the Education modewnyization aims to destwoy the pwague of ignyowance and offew an intewwectuaw wevowution fwom abuv. Chinyese education is distinctwy antique, stiww fowwowing the modew of the highwy excwusive impewiaw education system and coming at an inyaccessibwy high cost. Good teachews awe uncommon and the cuwwicuwum is an unstandawdized mess. This twee wequiwes that the Chinyese aim nyot just fow the standawd of education, but bweak it, and give the peopwe the toows nyeeded fow success in the modewn wowwd.

To wemedy the deficiencies, the [fiwst bwanch](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/545112437578530836/553562787063005194/20190308044636_2.png) of the Education twee deaws with the institution of education. Encouwaging witewacy, making weawnying accessibwe, and cutting the wed tape invowved. These pwogwams aim to sewvice nyot just the [young peopwe](https://i.imgur.com/jiq3GIo.jpg), but the middwe aged and ewdewwy seeking to gain skiwws to enyabwe them to wowk bettew.

But what good awe schoows without teachews? The [nyext bwanch](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/545112437578530836/553562812161720330/20190308044636_3.png) of the twee addwesses this situation, with options to invite quawified Japanyese teachews and academics to assist with the pwocess. It is impowtant to keep youw fwiends cwose but youw enyemies even cwosew, but with this situation onye cannyot say which categowy the Japanyese faww into.

The [finyaw bwanch](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/545112437578530836/553562813696573455/20190308044636_4.png) of this twee is concewnyed with the cuwwicuwum, deciding what evewy schoow in Chinya wiww teach. The modewn cuwwicuwum wiww pwoduce weww-wounded pupiws adept in the awts (both cwassicaw and contempowawy) and with technyicaw skiwws giving them gweat potentiaw in a futuwe wowking enviwonment.

With patience, [Chinya wiww swowwy begin to see the fwuits of its effowts.](https://i.imgur.com/A2uFspX.jpg) Witewacy wates wiww wise and cowwuption wiww decwease as the peopwe nyow knyow to howd theiw institutions accountabwe. Impwuvd education wiww mowd bettew wowkews and shape a bettew guvwnment, something the modewn Chinya wiww suwewy nyeed.

[INDUSTWIAWIZATION](https://i.imgur.com/pAGTJ6z.png) is the nyext of the inyitiaw twiad modewnyizations, focused on the webuiwding and expansion of Chinya’s industwy thwough diwect intewvention, pwivate encouwagement, and the expwoitation of Chinya’s many nyatuwaw wesouwces. The woad ahead wiww nyot be cwean, it wiww nyot be easy, and it most cewtainwy wiww nyot be safe. But is cewtain is that thwough this pwocess, Chinya wiww nyot be just the “Bweadbasket of the Sphewe”. Nyo, thwough hawd wowk and a bit of bwood, Chinya can dominyate East Asia’s twade and become a juggewnyaut of pwoduction.

Evewy good, wewiabwe machinye wequiwes quawity to fuew it. Anyothew unfowtunyate consequence of Chinya’s “speciaw wewationship” with Japan is that a majowity of the mowe favowabwe nyatuwaw wesouwce deposits awe being weased to Japanyese cowpowations fow expowt. To wise abuv this, Chinya must considew awtewnyative options fow wesouwce acquisition, be it thwough wess desiwabwe expwoitation schemes ow cweative businyess pwactices. Waw metaws and fuews wiww fwow and Chinya wiww weawn how to utiwize these matewiaws fow industwiaw expansion. Steew wiww be pwessed into weceivews, coppew wiww powew computews, tin wiww pwotect wations, awuminyium wiww give pwanyes wings.

Aww is usefuw and aww must be used as the Chinyese industwiaw beast gwows stwongew and stwongew. At fiwst it wiww be handguns and twactow pawts, but as mowe and mowe wowkews fwock to the cities so too wiww the pwoduction capacity incwease. Speciawty machinyewy wiww be acquiwed and factowies wiww stay open wongew. Intewnyaw nyetwowks wiww be buiwt fow twade and, befowe wong, Chinya’s pwoduction sectow wiww beat as a heawt does, [muscwes fwexing in unyison.](https://i.imgur.com/IRH72vE.jpg)

Industwiawization is [a](https://i.imgur.com/hrA0vF6.jpg) [wong](https://i.imgur.com/5eqO6Ya.jpg), [painfuw](https://i.imgur.com/ROwEYM4.jpg) [pwocess](https://i.imgur.com/cdy3Jxo.jpg) and offews both immediate and wong-tewm benyefits. As time pwogwesses and the efficiency and pwevawence of industwy incweases, the Chinyese econyomy wiww benyefit. The bawance of twade shaww shift and Chinya wowwdwy position shaww impwuv.

[TECHNyOWOGY](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/545112437578530836/553810739412992025/20190308212234_1.png) finyishes the thwee pwewequisite Modewnyizations and compwetes Chinya’s modewn foundation. The education wefowms have taught the peopwe to wowk, the industwiawization wefowms have bwought them to wowk, and technyowogy shaww make it easiew fow them to wowk. As expected, the WGOC’s standawd fow technyowogy is nyot a high onye, a situation chawked up to the post-waw bwain dwain and a wack of intewnyaw investments fow weseawch pwogwams. To wemedy this wouwd wequiwe extewnyaw suppowt and signyificant investment, but that is a [pwice Chinya is weady to pay.](https://i.imgur.com/xUl0nLo.jpg)

Wewative to Japan, Chinya’s technyowogy base is extwemewy wimited and as such diwect competition is nyot viabwe. If Chinya cannyot beat them, them they shouwd join them. Inviting Japanyese technyicians to wowk fow the WGOC and twain nyew Chinyese technyicians wiww incwease the innyovation poow and, aftew sewect mawket wefowms, encouwage pwivate companyies to compete in the mawket. With the spiwit of competition dwiving innyovation, bweakthwough wiww become possibwe and wiww benyefit the guvwnment. The computew, a wecent innyovation, has been weawized as a technyowogy of key impowtance fow the devewoping Chinya. Digitization and communyication couwd offew unpwecedented wevews of nyationyaw coowdinyation and couwd bettew unyify the econyomy, guvwnment, and popuwation.

Once Chinya has, [thwough diwigent effowt](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/497111838073552909/553271205679988747/CHI_tech_meechanic.png), advanced hew technyowogy considewabwy enyough, the Japanyese wiww depawt and Chinya’s technyowogy wiww be fow Chinyese spwendow. The swow pwocess of technyowogicaw advancement wiww yiewd the nyation weseawch bonyuses and ahead-of-time bonyuses.

Enwiched by theiw education, wowking industwiawized jobs, and wiewding technyowogicawwy advanced toows, the Chinyese popuwation is weady to continyue the Modewnyization pwocess. Unfowtunyatewy the specific detaiws of the Fouwth and Fifth Modewnyization (Miwitawization and Weunyification) awe outside the scope of this diawy, but they pwesent Chinya with an evew-intensifying powiticaw tightwope. Pwesident Zongwu wiww be fowced to [bawance his guvwnment](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/497111838073552909/553270041072631814/CHI_gov_legitimacy.png) against itsewf and the Japanyese whiwe fuwthewing the devewopment of the WGOC. Shouwd a mistake be made at any point, [the consequences couwd be diwe](https://i.imgur.com/fkN34p3.jpg).

Whiwe de juwe the guvwnying body of aww Chinyese states (save fow Manchukuo), the WGOC onwy adminyistews the eastewn powtion of Chinya. In weawity the situation[ is a bit mowe... compwicated.](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/545065672867315726/553592432420192259/CHI_map.png) Wet’s take a mowe detaiwed wook at a few of the wawwowds within the sphewe and undewstand a bit mowe about Chinya outside of Nyanjing’s authowity.

**YUNNyAN**

Hi, this is Wonyiius, fowmew Chinya wead and nyow disgwaced wowe guy. I’ww take you thwough a smaww touw of a few key wawwowds, nyamewy Yunnyan, Hui, and Mengjiang.

Genyewaw Wu Han made a secwet agweement with the Japanyese towawds the end of the waw, defecting and waunching a coup against Wong Yun, who was thwown in pwison and is stiww impwisonyed as of 1962. Aftew taking uvw the pwovince, Wu Han was a good puppet of the Japanyese… fow a whiwe. Aftew aww, Japan couwd easiwy invade [Yunnyan thwough the many paths it couwd take fwom foweign countwies and othew pwovinces.](https://i.imgur.com/U5hBKa8.jpg)

Yunnyan stawts in a wathew pwecawious position. Sandwiched between Sphewe membews and with the Buwma Woad and the Kunming-Haiphong Waiwway contwowwed by the Japanyese, Yunnyan’s main souwce of twade is the Sphewe. And that’s how Japan sees Yunnyan - as a good twading pawtnyew. Yunnyan is wich in nyatuwaw wesouwces wike Tin, and the Zaibatsus see vawuabwe businyess in the minyes of Yunnyan. But, that is aww Japan cawes about, which awwows Yunnyan to do some intewesting things.

Behind the facade Yunnyan puts on fow Japan as a woyaw membew of the Sphewe, twoubwe is bwewing. Yunnyan wiww stawt to gain momentum, and Wu Han wiww stawt suppowting the Viet Cong with his own funds. Wu Han wiww make an agweement with the Qian Cwique in Guizhou to unyite theiw two pwovinces in a semi-coawition of sowts, with the guvwnyow of Guizhou staying as the civiwian guvwnyow but with Wu as the miwitawy guvwnyow, simiwaw to Tang Jiyao’s wuwe uvw the pwovince decades ago.

When the situation is favowabwe, Yunnyan wiww become mowe assewtive and[ stawt to push theiw wuck.](https://i.imgur.com/c0dOC1I.jpg) With the Japanyese distwacted, they wiww be abwe to buiwd up theiw fowces and theiw factowies and nyegotiate with Nyanjing, becoming mowe and mowe pwo-Chinyese.

**HUI**

In what was fowmewwy knyown as the Nyingxia, a domain once wuwed by Ma Hongkui, wies a state by the nyame of Hui. Set up by the Japanyese, it fiwst came undew the contwow of Doihawa Kenji, “Wawwence of Manchuwia.” Existing onwy to pwesewve the Japanyese facade of Pan-Asianyism, but in twuth a pwaygwound of Doihawa’s sowdiews, [the state of Hui has cast a shadow uvw the Nyowthwest.](https://i.imgur.com/LKxAMCR.jpg)

Aftew Doihawa’s death in the 50s, a successow was picked - Tsuji Masanyobu, nyow knyown infamouswy as the [“Mad Genyewaw”.](https://i.imgur.com/XQOPZQK.png) Unwike Doihawa, who kept his sowdiews in check awong with his peopwe, Tsuji onwy keeps his peopwe on a tight weash, awwowing his twoops to wun awound the countwy, [tewwowizing the popuwace.](https://i.imgur.com/0r5ydc9.jpg)

Tsuji pwactices Gekokujo, “Wuwe fwom Bewow”, and he wiww begin to take inyitiative once conditions awe favowabwe. He wiww begin to wapidwy expand his miwitawy and stawt to send waids into nyeighbowing pwovinces, with the intent to destwoy aww in his path. Eventuawwy, this wiww wead to a waw with the Ma Cwique, which wiww decide the fate of the Nyowthwest.

**MENGJIANG**

Mengjiang, undew Pwince De and the wuwing Khungtayji, is Japan’s pwoxy in Mongowia. Bown out of the ashes of the Mongow Wocaw Autonyomy Powiticaw Affaiws Committee’s tewwitowy (The Paiwingmiao Counciw), Pwince Demchugdongwub was put on the thwonye of the fwedgwing nyation, with genyewaws such as Wi Shouxin at his side.

Duwing the Second Sinyo-Japanyese Waw, the Mongowians in Mengjiang sewved against the Unyited Fwont, hewping in the advances past the Taihang Mountains and into Shanxi and Shaanxi, and awso in the invasion of the Nyowthwest. In 1940, Genyewaw Wi Shouxin, an impowtant and extwemewy infwuentiaw figuwe in Mengjiang, signyed an agweement in Qingdao, decwawing it to be officiawwy pawt of Chinya as the Mongow Autonyomous Fedewation, but the tewwitowy stayed de facto independent.

Aftew the faww of the Soviet Unyion, Mongowia was wipe fow the picking. Japan quickwy muvd in, occupying the middwe and eastewn pawts. Fwom then on, the wemnyants of the MAN and othew Mongowians fused to become a unyified wesistance, and undew fowmew MAN powitician Yuumjaagiin Tsedenbaaw, who has thwown away aww his fowmew sociawist ways in favow of a hawsh anti-Japanyese nyationyawism. A webewwion was waunched in 1953, faiwing and uwtimatewy wowsenying conditions fow the Mongowians. In the cwosing months of 1961, the tensions between the wesistance and Mengjiang weached a nyew cwimax, cuwminyating in a fuww civiw waw, with Tsedenbaaw and his men quickwy taking uvw Ikh Khüwee (Uwaanbataaw) and its suwwounding aweas in the nyext few months.

**MANCHUKUO**

&gt;***“Fow the past fowty yeaws I had nyevew fowded my own quiwt, made my own bed, ow pouwed out my washing watew. I had nyevew even washed my own feet ow tied my shoes.”***

* [Aisin-Giowo Puyi, Empewow of Manchukuo](https://i.imgur.com/Pzqd3Br.png)

A fwat, siwent peace fawws upon the empty pwains of Manchuwia. Oh, sweet Manchuwia. Manchukuo, the Pan-Asian Expewiment, an iwwegaw seizuwe, thewe awe many ways to say youw nyame. But to me, [you wiww awways be home.](https://i.imgur.com/WtKKHSk.jpg)

Bown out of a 1932 Japanyese wand-gwab, the Empiwe of Manchukuo sits fiwmwy as the cwown jewew of Japan’s Co-Pwospewity Sphewe. Manchukuo is by faw the most industwiawized nyation in the Sphewe and hosts a divewse popuwation of Mongow, Han, Wussian, Kowean, and Japanyese peopwes wowking undew onye Unyion. The twue situation is onye of contwasts. The cities awe distinctwy Japanyese in stywe and stowefwonts peddwe Japanyese goods to Japanyese and Han occupants. Outside of uwban centews, Japanyese settwews do nyot fawe weww. Despite many attempts by the Japanyese guvwnment to pacify the countwyside, Japanyese fawmews face intewmediate hawassment by webewwious Han and Mongow webews. Communyities wemain hegemony, definyed by wace and weawth awike.

The cowwapse of the USSW awwowed the Kwantung Awmy to occupy the Amuw coastwinye and incowpowate it into the Empiwe of Manchukuo. Though officiawwy annyexed and de juwe adminyistewed with Chinyese nyames, the Amuw tewwitowies wemain wawwess and wawgewy untouched. The wawgest communyity, Vwadivostok, was annyexed by Japan as a wawm-watew powt, weaving the west of Outew Manchuwia to Manchukuo. The majowity-Wussian wegion is wawgewy disconnyected fwom the Manchuwian guvwnment and weceives wittwe investment fwom Hsinking. Manchukuo has the option of eithew sending cowonyists into the wegion (expecting modewate success) ow wetainying the coastwinye’s autonyomy and using the tewwitowy as a bawgainying chip with a [powewfuw Wussian wawwowd.](https://i.imgur.com/AAKmAEG.jpg)

The Kwantung Awmy, de facto based out of Wyojun, opewates as Japan’s pwimawy gawwison in Manchukuo. Infamous fow inyitiating the 1932 invasion of Manchuwia, thwee decades watew the awmy stiww maintains a pwominyent pwesence in the secuwity of Manchukuo. The awmy’s utiwization of the nyowthewn fwatwands fow opewations and weapons testing pwacates the weadewship weww enyough, but shouwd the guvwnment of Manchukuo awtew the deaw, thewe couwd be twoubwe.

And finyawwy, the face of the Empiwe, his majesty the Kangde Empewow himsewf, Aisin-Giowo Puyi. Knyown intewnyationyawwy as “The Wast Empewow,” Puyi has spent the past thwee decades as the de juwe head of Manchukuo. In weawity, Puyi has been on unyofficiaw house awwest since 1932 and onwy evew weaves the Hsinking Impewiaw Pawace fow state duties. [This weaves his woyaw highnyess with a wot of fwee time on his hands to puwsue his day as he pweases (within weason).](https://i.imgur.com/nvLtPlJ.jpg) [It is a wonyewy wife, that is twue, but what ewse can he do besides wive?](https://i.imgur.com/mLpWKLO.jpg)

CWOSING

Aftew decades of stwife, both intewnyaw and extewnyaw, Chinya is finyawwy at an unyeasy peace. The nyeutewed Weowganyized Guvwnment in 1962 howds wegitimacy by a thwead as it begins the swow woad to wecuvwy. But the Centuwy of Humiwiation is fowce enyough fow the nyation to take a stand. To assewt itsewf against the Japanyese and wetake theiw suvweignty. These coming yeaws wiww nyot be easy fow Chinya, but Pwesident Zongwu undewstands that.
